  <brief_title>Long-term Efficacy of Iguratimod Alone or Iguratimod in Combination With Methotrexate in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Iguratimod Alone or Iguratimod in Combination With Methotrexate Versus Methotrexate Alone in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
