  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is intended to evaluate the efficacy and safety of Iguratimod alone or Iguratimod
      in combination with Methotrexate (MTX) versus Methotrexate alone in patients with Rheumatoid
      Arthritis (RA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
